  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">UWC Costa Rica is a high school like no other!  We believe in the power of innovative education to drive positive social transformation. We bring together an intentionally diverse community of 194 students from 125+ nationalities, 82% of whom receive scholarship support.  Grounded in experiential education, our students live, dream, and learn together.  They are empowered to look beyond prejudice and labels and instead connect through their shared humanity to address local and global challenges.</narrative>
